<section class="bg-white py-12 lg:py-16 border-t border-slate-100">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-center">Why Gate 1 is Public Info & Remote Only</h3>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Reason 1 - Independence</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Site visits create implicit relationships with developers. 
            The remote analysis maintains strict independence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
           <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Reason 2 - Efficiency</h4>
           <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            Public filings contain 70-80% of critical risk indicators. 
            Traveling to site before analyzing public data is wasteful.
           </p>
        </div>

        <div>
           <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Reason 3 - Decision Protection</h4>
           <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
            If public data reveals deal-breaking silences, you avoid sunk costs of site visits, NDAs, and LOIs.
           </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
